<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220569>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Macronemus analis (Pascoe, 1866). 1 – 2, females dorsal view; 3, male fifth urosternite; 4, female fifth urosternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220569/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220570>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 11. Macronemus rufescens (Bates, 1862). 5 – 6, holotype, male: 5, dorsal view; 6, labels; 7 – 8, male: 7, fifth urosternite; 8, protibial spine; 9 – 11, female: 9, dorsal view; 10, fifth urosternite; 11, profemora with inferior margin projected near base and longitudinal, glabrous band." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220570/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220571>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 17. Macronemus giuglarisi sp. nov. 12, holotype, male, dorsal view; 13, male, dorsal view; 14, male fifth urosternite; 15, female fifth urosternite; 16, male protibia with a long apical spine; 17, female protibia apex slightly projected, without spine." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220577>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43 – 47. Alphus similis Martins, 1985. 43 – 45, male: 43, dorsal view; 44, fifth urosternite; 45, detail of the antennomere 11 modified at the apex; 46 – 47, female: 46, dorsal view; 47, fifth urosternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220577/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220578>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48 – 51. Pseudaethomerus lacordairei (Bates, 1862). 48 – 49, male: 48, dorsal view; 49, fifth urosternite; 50 – 51, female: 50, dorsal view; 51, fifth urosternite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220578/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

